#######In the server where the node are present( Server 1)#################
1. Run the getNodes.sh to get details of all started nodes into allNodes.job

    usage : sh getNodes.sh

2. Run the getsimnodes.sh to get details of specific type of nodes into selNodes.txt.

        usage: sh getsimnodes.sh BSC

3. Run the filterNodes.sh to filter the BSC nodes from the allNodes.job into nodeips.txt.

            usage: sh filterNodes.sh allNodes.job selNodes.txt

4. copy the nodeips.txt file to other server where the scripts are present(server-2).

####### In the server where the scripts are present(server-2) ##############
5. Run trigger.sh to execute the OPS commands on the nodes.

6. Observe the results in the totalstat.log .
